# Coffee Shop Menu

A static coffee shop menu webpage designed using HTML and inline CSS styling.

## 📌 Features

- Categorized menu sections
- Styled headings and pricing alignment
- Themed color scheme
- Structured layout formatting

## 🛠 Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3 (Inline Styling)

## 🚀 How to Run

1. Open the HTML file in a web browser.
2. View the menu layout and design.

## 🎯 Purpose

This project was created to practice:
- Page layout structuring
- Styling text and backgrounds
- Using inline CSS
- Organizing content visually

